casebody.head_matter:
PMCM TV, LLC, petitioner,
v.
FEDERAL COMMUNICATIONS COMMISSION, et al.
No. 18-717.
Supreme Court of the United States
Feb. 19, 2019.
Motion of petitioner to defer consideration of the petition for a writ of certiorari denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.
THE CHIEF JUSTICE and Justice KAVANAUGH took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
